Titolo: Disaster Report 4 Plus: Summer Memories

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Disaster Report 4 Plus: Summer Memories is an action-adventure game developed by Granzella, released in 2018 in Japan for the PlayStation 4. It is the fourth entry in the Disaster Report series and was originally meant to be released for the PlayStation 3; its production was halted in 2011, three days after the 2011 T≈çhoku earthquake and tsunami, but resumed with a new publisher in 2014. A Nintendo Switch version was released in September 2019.